hey yall! my day has been awesome..

biology- did a boring packet. fun stuff

math- took a test. blah.

lunch- same o same o

math lab- we did a weird newspaper activity, and my hands got all icky and black!

world history- learned about the world. and history. hince the name WORLD HISTORY! lol and then we found out that my language teacher is ordering pizza for our class tomorrow because we had the highest average on our culture components, because we are genius's! no joke.

went to church right after school. finished my biology homework. and then ate dinner. then rob came and ate with me. he is sooo HA-larious! like no joke. then brooke came and sat with us, and then michael came, and then heather came, and then sarah came.. and then right before i knew it.. we had a party! lol me and heather.. or excuse me.. heather and i established that michael and rob are not in college. oh yeah and that the bread we have on wednesday nights are rolls not buiscuits! *cough michael cough* =) all this stuff happened BEFORE Primetime.. wow! then we had Primetime, but michael told heather and i that adam and chris were going to be there.. so we weren't planning on singing. and then adam and chris never showed up, so heather and i ended up singing that night! we just stayed cool and winged it! but wow what an AMAZING DAY!! and then brooke carson sat on me. lol and at the end of Primetime, Lynn said tell everyone that you love them and give them a hug and stuff.. so then i do that.. and i walk out the door, and bruce comes up to me and says i love you jennifer.. and i turned around and gave him a hug, but i accidentally said i love you too brooke.. when i meant to say bruce! ugh. im sorry bruce! ttyl everyone!

much love, jennifer
